《'''The Partner ～給摯愛的百年朋友～'''》（{{lang-ja|The Partner ～愛しき百年の友へ～}}、{{lang-vi|Người cộng sự}}）是一部[[日本|日本]]與[[越南|越南]]合拍的[[電視劇|電視劇]]，於2013年9月29日，分別在[[TBS電視台|TBS電視台]]和[[越南電視台|越南電視台]]播出<ref>日方確定為當天晚間九點播出，越方則是當地時間晚間七點。</ref>。本劇由[[東山紀之|東山紀之]]、[[范黃東|范黃東]]主演，為紀念[[日本|日本]]與[[越南|越南]]建交40週年的慶祝活動之一，同時兩家電視台也是初次合作。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/13/5/14/n3870525.htm | title=東山紀之秀英語越南語 蘆田愛菜緊張 | publisher=大紀元 | date=2013-05-14 | accessdate=2016-04-28 | author1=汪青怡 | language=zh | archive-date=2016-06-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602145754/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/13/5/14/n3870525.htm | dead-url=no }}[http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/5/14/n3870525.htm |date=20160602144221 }} {{zh-cn}}]</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2024540/full/ | language=ja | script-title=東山紀之、日本・ベトナム共同制作国交ドラマに一人二役で主演 | publisher=[[Oricon|Oricon]] |